data.text: Thanks for reading the November issue of Yellow Bike Magazine! Want to support the zine as well as our films? We have a goal to be able to make films full time and things are getting to the point where this path is becoming more clear and attainable for us. I would seriously love it if you'd check out Yellow Bike's Patreon page. Lots of great BTS, early access to everything, films the public doesn't see, exclusive merch, tutorials and much more. This is an amazing way that you can help us achieve our goals and dreams of being full time creators. patreon.com/yellowbikefilms instagram/youtube/twitter/facebook: @yellowbikefilms yellowbikefilms@gmail.com
